metadata.name: Echoes of the Infinite
metadata.description: "Echoes of the Infinite" is a generative artwork created through the use of Javascript code. The composition consists of a series of geometric shapes and lines arranged in a semi-random pattern. Randomness creates an organic and unpredictable quality. The contrasting colors and shapes create a dynamic image that suggests a cosmic and expansive theme. The title, "Echoes of the Infinite", invites the viewer to contemplate the infinite possibilities and beauty of the universe.
